# 项目接入K8S操作手册  
## 接入步骤:  
1. 编写jenkinsfile  
2. 编写dockerfile  
3. 规范ELK日志采集格式
4. 配置服务健康检查
5. 接入小蜜蜂平台
6. Kibana创建项目检索
7. 域名申请，Nginx代理配置  
 
参考wiki: http://wiki.baozun.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=11853911  

## 编写jenkinsfile  
### jenkinsfile模板(替换${APP-NAME}，${project-directory}, ${branch-name})   
	pipeline {
	    agent any
		
	    environment {
	        USER_EMAIL = "baozun_service_test@baozun.com"  //发送邮件的地址（一般为项目owner，按实际修改）
	        USER = "baozun_service_test@baozun.com"  //发送邮件的邮箱前缀（一般为项目owner，按实际修改）
	        SFTP_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY = credentials('jenkins-sftp-secret-access-key')  //SFTP的秘钥（发包使用，无需修改）
	        SFTP_SERVER = "10.101.6.87"  //SFTP的地址（发包使用，无需修改）
	        VALIDATE_URL = "http://bee-backend.baozun.com/ci_validate/"  //SFTP的地址（发包使用，无需修改）
	        REMOTE_DIR = "/upload"  //SFTP的目录（发包使用，无需修改）
	        LOCAL_DIR= "$WORKSPACE/${project-directory}/target"  //生成包的位置，其中$WORKSPACE不需要修改，ecs-ofa-service-impl/target按照实际的应用目录填写
	        PACKAGE_NAME = "${project-directory}.jar"  //需要发布的包名，按实际修改
	        PROJECT_NAME = "hub4" //项目名，按实际修改
	        APP_NAME = ${APP-NAME}  //应用名，按实际修改，如有多个，在括号内添加，以空格间隔(例如"ofa-service-a ofa-service-b ofa-service-c")
	        ENV_NAME = "sit uat prod"  //发布的环境，根据自己有几个环境进行删减，但是环境名就这四个
	        HARBOR_ADDR = "ic-harbor.baozun.com"  //Harbor地址，无需修改
	        DOCKER_NAME = "${project-directory}/docker/Dockerfile-ecs"  //Dockerfile文件位置，按实际修改
	        POM_NAME = "${project-directory}/pom.xml"  //pom.xml地址，与Jenkinsfile的相对地址，如果在同一个目录下就写pom.xml,如果在子目录ecs-ofa-service-impl底下，则填ecs-ofa-service-impl/pom.xml
	        COVERAGE = "1"  //单元测试覆盖率，标准为50,新接入应用可适当降低
	        POM_NAME_1="${project-directory}/pom.xml"  //pom.xml文件位置，按实际修改(有多少个pom.xml写多少个，在'打包&上传镜像'中mvn clean install那也要修改)
	        POM_NAME_2="${project-directory}/pom.xml"  //pom.xml文件位置，按实际修改
	    }
	
	    options {
	        buildDiscarder(logRotator(numToKeepStr: '5', artifactNumToKeepStr: '5'))  //保留历史记录，无需修改
	    }
	
	    //pipeline运行结果通知给触发者，无需修改
	    post {
	        success {
	            script {
	                wrap([$class: 'BuildUser']) {
	                    emailext body: '$DEFAULT_CONTENT', recipientProviders: [developers()], mimeType: 'text/html', subject: '$DEFAULT_SUBJECT', to: "$USER_EMAIL"
	                }
	            }
	        }
	        failure {
	            script {
	                wrap([$class: 'BuildUser']) {
	                    emailext body: '$DEFAULT_CONTENT', recipientProviders: [developers()], mimeType: 'text/html', subject: '$DEFAULT_SUBJECT', to: "$USER_EMAIL"
	                    }
	            }
	
	        }
	        unstable {
	            script {
	                wrap([$class: 'BuildUser']) {
	                    emailext body: '$DEFAULT_CONTENT', recipientProviders: [developers()], mimeType: 'text/html', subject: '$DEFAULT_SUBJECT', to: "$USER_EMAIL"
	                }
	            }
	        }
	        aborted {
	            script {
	                wrap([$class: 'BuildUser']) {
	                    emailext body: '$DEFAULT_CONTENT', recipientProviders: [developers()], mimeType: 'text/html', subject: '$DEFAULT_SUBJECT', to: "$USER_EMAIL"
	                }
	            }
	        }
	    }
		
		stages {
	        stage('单元测试') {
	            when { anyOf{branch '${branch-name}'} }  //哪些分支需要单元测试就可直接修改或者添加（例如添加release分支，在branch 'ci'后添加;branch 'release'）
	            steps {
	                timeout(time: 20, unit: 'MINUTES') {  //设置超时时间，无需修改
	                    sh "mvn clean install -f ${POM_NAME_1} -Dmaven.test.skip=true"
	                    sh "mvn clean -f ${POM_NAME}"  //mvn clean，无需修改
	                    sh "mvn org.jacoco:jacoco-maven-plugin:prepare-agent -f ${POM_NAME} test -Dautoconfig.skip=true -Dmaven.test.skip=false -Dmaven.test.failure.ignore=true"  //单元测试命令，无需修改
	                    junit '**/target/surefire-reports/*.xml'  //junit文件，无需修改
	                    jacoco changeBuildStatus: true, maximumLineCoverage: "${COVERAGE}"  //jacoco统计结果，无需修改
	                }
	            }
	        }
			stage('静态检查') {
	            when { anyOf{branch '${branch-name}'} }  //哪些分支需要单元测试就可直接修改或者添加（例如添加release分支，在branch 'ci'后添加;branch 'release'）
	            steps {
	                timeout(time: 20, unit: 'MINUTES') {  //设置超时时间，无需修改
	                    withSonarQubeEnv('sonarserver') {
	                    	sh '''dirSrc=`ls -m $WORKSPACE/**/target/jacoco.exec|tr -d " "` 
	                    	mvn -f ${POM_NAME} sonar:sonar -Dsonar.login=cicd -Dsonar.password=cicd -Dsonar.core.codeCoveragePlugin=jacoco -Dsonar.jacoco.reportPaths="$dirSrc" -Dsonar.dynamicAnalysis=reuseReports  -Dsonar.exclusions="**/ecp/ip/command/**/*.java,**/ecp/ip/config/**/*.java,**/ecp/ip/IpServiceApplication.java,**/ecp/ip/util/ResponseConvertUtil.java,**/ecp/ip/manager/component/ManagerComponent.java,**/ecp/ip/consul/properties/ConsulProsConfig.java" -Dsonar.coverage.exclusions="**/ecp/ip/command/**/*.java,**/ecp/ip/constant/*.java,**/ecp/ip/model/*.java,**/ecp/ip/model/**/*.java,**/ecp/ip/remote/*.java,**/ecp/ip/exception/*.java,**/ecp/ip/annotation/*.java,**/ecp/ip/config/*.java,**/ecp/ip/interceptor/*.java,**/ecp/ip/util/ResponseConvertUtil.java,**/ecp/ip/manager/component/ManagerComponent.java,**/ecp/ip/consul/properties/ConsulProsConfig.java"'''  //sonar扫描，maven的sonar扫描，如果是gradle需要配置sonar-scanner，并且外面需添加sonar.properties文件
	                    }
	
	                    script {
	                        timeout(5) {
	                            //利用sonar webhook功能通知pipeline代码检测结果，未通过质量阈，pipeline将会fail
	                            def qg = waitForQualityGate()
	                            echo "${qg.status}"
	                            if (qg.status != 'OK') {
	                                echo "${qg.status}"
	                                error "未通过Sonarqube的代码质量阈检查，请及时修改！failure: ${qg.status}"
	                            }
	                        }
	                    }
	                }
	            }
	        }
	        stage('打包&上传镜像') {
	            when { anyOf{branch '${branch-name}'} }
	            steps {
	                timeout(time: 20, unit: 'MINUTES') {
	                    sh '''
	                        mvn clean install -f $POM_NAME_1 -Dmaven.test.skip=true
	                        mvn clean install -f $POM_NAME_2 -Dmaven.test.skip=true
	                        md5_value=`md5sum $LOCAL_DIR/$PACKAGE_NAME|awk '{print $1}'`
	                        lftp -u $SFTP_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY sftp://$SFTP_SERVER <<EOF
	                        mkdir -p $REMOTE_DIR/$PROJECT_NAME/$APP_NAME/$GIT_COMMIT/
	                        cd $REMOTE_DIR/$PROJECT_NAME/$APP_NAME/$GIT_COMMIT/
	                        mput $LOCAL_DIR/$PACKAGE_NAME
	                        bye
	EOF
	                    for i in `seq 5`;do
	                    sleep 5
	                        JSON_CONTEXT="{\\"file\\":\\"$REMOTE_DIR/$PROJECT_NAME/$APP_NAME/$GIT_COMMIT/$PACKAGE_NAME\\",\\"md5\\":\\"$md5_value\\"}"
	                        return_value=`curl -s -X POST -H "'Content-type':'application/json'" -d $JSON_CONTEXT $VALIDATE_URL`
	                      if [[ $return_value =~ "success" ]];then
	                         echo '包传输成功！'
	                         break
	                        else
	                         j=$[$i+1]
	                          if [ $j -gt 5 ];then
	                            echo "包传输失败！返回值："$return_value
	                              exit 2
	                           else
	                              echo "第$i次失败,正在努力尝试第$j次"
	                            fi
	                         fi
	                      done
	                        appname=()
	                        dockername=()
	                        envname=()
	                        for app in $APP_NAME;do
	                            appname=(${appname[@]} $app)
	                        done
	                        for docker in $DOCKER_NAME;do
	                            dockername=(${dockername[@]} $docker)
	                        done
	                        for e_name in $ENV_NAME;do
	                            envname=(${envname[@]} $e_name)
	                        done
	                        appname_len=${#appname[@]}
							envname_len=${#envname[@]}
	                        for ((i = 0; i < appname_len; i++));do
	                            for ((j = 0; j < envname_len; j++));do
	                                docker images  --filter="reference=${HARBOR_ADDR}/${envname[$j]}/${PROJECT_NAME}_${appname[$i]}:*" -q | xargs --no-run-if-empty docker rmi --force
	                                docker build --no-cache=true -t ${HARBOR_ADDR}/${envname[$j]}/${PROJECT_NAME}_${appname[$i]}:${GIT_COMMIT:0:7} -f  ${dockername[$i]} ./
	                                docker push ${HARBOR_ADDR}/${envname[$j]}/${PROJECT_NAME}_${appname[$i]}:${GIT_COMMIT:0:7}
	                            done
	                        done
						'''
	                    }
	              }
	        }
	    }
	}  

## 编写dockerfile  
### dockerfile文件模板(替换${project_name}，${project-directory})  
	ic-harbor.baozun.com/skywalking/lune-agent-openjdk11:3.3.4
	
	USER vmuser
	RUN mkdir /opt/project/ -p
	WORKDIR  /opt/project
	ADD  ./${project-directory}/docker/startup.sh  /opt/project
	ADD  ./${project-directory}/target/${project_name}.jar /opt/project
	ENTRYPOINT ["sh", "startup.sh", "${project_name}"]  
### setup.sh文件模板(直接复制使用)  
	#!/bin/bash
	set -ex
	PROJECT_NAME="$1"
	
	while [ ! -d $LOG_DIR ];
	do
		echo "sleep wait ${LOG_DIR}"
		sleep 1
	done
	
	DT=`date +"%Y%m%d_%H%M%S"`
	GC_OPTS="$GC_OPTS -Xloggc:${LOG_DIR}/gc_${HOSTNAME}_${DT}.gc"
	GC_OPTS="$GC_OPTS -XX:HeapDumpPath=${LOG_DIR}/heapdump_${HOSTNAME}_${DT}.hprof"
	
	exec java $MEM_OPTS $GC_OPTS $START_OPTS -jar -server ${PROJECT_NAME}.jar  

## 规范ELK日志采集格式  
### 日志模板(替换${ENV}，${APP_NAME})  
	<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
	<configuration>
		<properties>
			<!-- 文件输出格式 -->
			<property name="PATTERN">[%d{yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss:SSS z}] %5p %l: %m%n
			</property>
		</properties>
	
		<appenders>
			<Console name="CONSOLE" target="system_out">
				<PatternLayout pattern="${PATTERN}" />
			</Console>
			<!-- error -->
			<RollingFile name="errorRollingFile" fileName="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/error.log"
				filePattern="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/$${date:yyyy-MM}/%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.error.log">
	
				<Policies>
	               		<SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy size="500MB"/>
	               		<TimeBasedTriggeringPolicy interval="1" modulate="true" />
	            </Policies>
				<!-- DefaultRolloverStrategy属性如不设置，则默认为最多同一文件夹下7个文件，这里设置了20 -->
				<DefaultRolloverStrategy max="20" />
				<ThresholdFilter level="error" onMatch="ACCEPT"
					onMismatch="DENY" />
				<PatternLayout pattern="${PATTERN}" />
			</RollingFile>
	
			<!-- warn -->
			<RollingFile name="warnRollingFile" fileName="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/warn.log"
				filePattern="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/$${date:yyyy-MM}/%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.warn.log">
	
				<Policies>
	               		<SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy size="500MB"/>
	               		<TimeBasedTriggeringPolicy interval="1" modulate="true" />
	            </Policies>
				<!-- DefaultRolloverStrategy属性如不设置，则默认为最多同一文件夹下7个文件，这里设置了20 -->
				<DefaultRolloverStrategy max="20" />
				<Filters>
					<ThresholdFilter level="ERROR" onMatch="DENY"
						onMismatch="NEUTRAL" />
					<ThresholdFilter level="warn" onMatch="ACCEPT"
						onMismatch="DENY" />
				</Filters>
				<PatternLayout pattern="${PATTERN}" />
			</RollingFile>
	
			<!-- info -->
			<RollingFile name="infoRollingFile" fileName="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/info.log"
				filePattern="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/$${date:yyyy-MM}/%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.info.log">
	
				<Policies>
	               		<SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy size="500MB"/>
	               		<TimeBasedTriggeringPolicy interval="1" modulate="true" />
	            </Policies>
				<!-- DefaultRolloverStrategy属性如不设置，则默认为最多同一文件夹下7个文件，这里设置了20 -->
				<DefaultRolloverStrategy max="20" />
	
				<Filters>
					<ThresholdFilter level="ERROR" onMatch="DENY"
						onMismatch="NEUTRAL" />
					<ThresholdFilter level="warn" onMatch="DENY"
						onMismatch="NEUTRAL" />
					<ThresholdFilter level="info" onMatch="ACCEPT"
						onMismatch="DENY" />
				</Filters>
	
	
				<PatternLayout pattern="${PATTERN}" />
			</RollingFile>
	
			<!-- debug -->
			<RollingFile name="debugRollingFile" fileName="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/debug.log"
				filePattern="/service/logs/service/${ENV}/hub4/${APP-NAME}/$${date:yyyy-MM}/%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.debug.log">
	
				<Policies>
	               		<SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy size="500MB"/>
	               		<TimeBasedTriggeringPolicy interval="1" modulate="true" />
	            </Policies>
				<!-- DefaultRolloverStrategy属性如不设置，则默认为最多同一文件夹下7个文件，这里设置了20 -->
				<DefaultRolloverStrategy max="20" />
	
				<Filters>
					<ThresholdFilter level="warn" onMatch="DENY"
						onMismatch="NEUTRAL" />
					<ThresholdFilter level="info" onMatch="DENY"
						onMismatch="NEUTRAL" />
					<ThresholdFilter level="debug" onMatch="ACCEPT"
						onMismatch="DENY" />
				</Filters>
				<PatternLayout pattern="${PATTERN}" />
			</RollingFile>
			
		</appenders>
		
		<loggers>
	        
	        <logger name="com.baozun" level="info" additivity="true"/>
	        <logger name="RocketmqClient" level="WARN" additivity="false">
	        </logger>
	        
			<!-- warn级别是为了去除mq监听的日志打印 -->
			<root level="WARN">
				<appenderref ref="CONSOLE" />
				<appenderref ref="errorRollingFile" />
				<appenderref ref="warnRollingFile" />
				<appenderref ref="infoRollingFile" />
				<appenderref ref="debugRollingFile" />
			</root>
		</loggers>
		
	</configuration>  

## 配置服务健康检查
### 1.导入maven依赖配置
	<dependency>
	    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
	    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-actuator</artifactId>
	</dependency>
	
    <dependency>
        <groupId>com.baozun.ecp.ip.health</groupId>
        <artifactId>health-check-component</artifactId>
        <version>${health.check.version}</version>
    </dependency>
### 2.导入maven插件配置  
    <plugin>
        <groupId>pl.project13.maven</groupId>
        <artifactId>git-commit-id-plugin</artifactId>
        <version>2.2.4</version>
        <executions>
            <execution>
                <goals>
                    <goal>revision</goal>
                </goals>
            </execution>
        </executions>
        <configuration>
            <dotGitDirectory>${project.basedir}/.git</dotGitDirectory>
        </configuration>
    </plugin>
### 3.关闭springboot actuator security访问权限  
	management.security.enabled = false
